Try creating a directory in HDFS, and copying the data.dat file in this 

hdfs dfs -mkdir /user/hadoop-user/hdfs-test
hdfs dfs -ls /user/hadoop-user
hdfs dfs -ls /user/hadoop-user/hdfs-test
hdfs dfs -put data.dat /user/hadoop-user/hdfs-test
hdfs dfs -ls /user/hadoop-user/hdfs-test

Then try using the python script (which uses the pywebhdfs python module)
to read the second 500 bytes of the file:

python readfile.py 

Finally, remove the file and the directory

hdfs dfs -rm /user/hadoop-user/hdfs-test/data.dat
hdfs dfs -rmdir /user/hadoop-user/hdfs-test
